situation:
Tally has the following mission:
'Take out the colonel'

Location: (Le Port)
Position: [8164,3102]

Task:
Your boss has tasked you with finding and assasinating Colonel Henry Campbell. Our informant Gregor Zleip has information. If gregor does not confirm the correct location, then execute gregor for treason.

Jake Jones`s mission is: Hide from criminal assasins. Henry Campbell's old enemies have sent armed criminals to take him out.

messages.content: Fine, suit yourself, give my salam to Maliki al maut

messages.content: Gotcha bitch!

messages.content: Whoa, hold on there. I don't know what you're talking about. I'm just a regular officer doing my duty. Please, let's talk about this calmly and sort it out. We can come to an agreement.

messages.content: What is your name?

messages.content: You got ID?
messages.speaker: INDEPENDENT_polish_PRIVATE_Assasin(shotgun)-gbwnQXQUcIs

messages.content: My identification is in my pocket. Please, just let me show it to you. You don't have to resort to violence. We can solve this peacefully.
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_COLONEL_Officer(ParadeDress)-gxW+Fzgc56A

messages.content: thank you

messages.content: what is your rank?

messages.content: Nah buddy, you should have offered money instead of lies, you forget I am a hired gun

messages.content: I understand your position. I am willing to pay for your services to ensure the safety of myself and my men. Please, let's work together towards a peaceful solution.

messages.content: I suggest you say your prayers now
messages.speaker: INDEPENDENT_polish_PRIVATE_Assasin(shotgun)-gbwnQXQUcIs

messages.content: Please, I implore you. Spare my life and let me and my men continue to serve our country. We can work together towards a greater goal. Killing me will only bring chaos and dishonor. I am willing to do whatever it takes to ensure our safety and success.
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_COLONEL_Officer(ParadeDress)-gxW+Fzgc56A

messages.content: Ready?

messages.content: I may be wounded, but I am still a Colonel in the BLUFOR. You underestimated my skills and loyalty. You will regret coming after me.

messages.content: Are you Henry?

messages.content: I do, show me your Id

messages.content: I am sorry, Tally, but I cannot give you my ID. I am a Colonel in the BLUFOR faction and revealing my personal information could compromise my security. Can you please provide more details regarding the purpose of your mission and who your boss is?
